info.description:
GRNRY 0.5 API Collection including sample tests.

##Important env vars:

*Auth API*
auth_url = https://grnry.api.io/
username = someuser
password = somepw

*Belt API*
belt_url = https://grnry.api.io/

*Profile API*
profile_url = https://grnry.api.io/

*EventStore API*
event_store_url = https://grnry.api.io/

*SCDF API*
scdf_url = https://grnry.api.io/

*Snowplow API*
snowplow_url = https://grnry.api.io/

##Tests

After each request the a base test is run:

var skipTest = pm.globals.get("skip_collection_test");

if (!skipTest) {
    pm.test("Status code is 200", function() {
        pm.response.to.have.status(200);
});
} else {
    console.log("Skipping status code 200 check")
}


*Note:*
Test case collections should be ran seperately due to the usage of postman.NextRequest() to retry requests. This will cause jumping over request if multiple test cases are ran together.

